product.longDescription:
Our instantly-iconic Outline Pro polypropylene collection takes you confidently in the direction of your destination thanks to its elevated design and eye-catching color options. This smart and sleek piece is all systems go – while pulling out all the stops: from its molded trolley handle to easy-lift top and side grips, major touchpoints are treated with Sam-AMH™ technology to help keep hands clean. With integrated extras like a built-in TSA lock and USB port (available in carry-on sizes only), as well as superb-adaptable interior lined in our eco-conscious Recyclex® fabric, this all-time travel essential bridges form and function flawlessly. Bordering on genius. Say it to yourself: You’ve earned this upgrade.
• Ergonomic retractable trolley handle with multi-stop Right Height™ adjustability
• Smooth, dual spinner wheels for easy handling and long-haul travel across any surface
• Durable polypropylene shell constructed in a clean, contemporary design
• Recyclex® interior liner fabric made from 100% recycled plastic bottles
• Innovative multi-functional KompressPak™ panel divider offers a compression system creating a neat organization while providing additional space to add more last minute souvenirs.
• Our unique KompressPak™ divider also comprises with a lining zippered pocket for your small odds and ends, while the secondary WetPak™ zippered pocket keeps damp items contained
• Built-in TSA lock with an integrated USB port (carry-on sizes only) and internal battery pocket
• Samsonite Antimicrobial Handle (Sam-AMH™) technology infused with a proprietary antimicrobial additive on trolley grip and top / side carry handles, which works to continuously suppress the growth of bacteria / mold to prevent degradation of the handling
